        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> as an evil 59 bard, i enjoy mortal kombat we own in duel and dont pull any of that they'll be lame and run off thats our biggest bonus just like necros have dots we have speed :-P, i've lost to a necro once, he was really good and i had crap resists, land snare and its all done, at 51 assume he isnt good at dueling and has poor resists, definatly have shadow step and a cos if yeah can, at 49 we get a selo's that lasts 2 minutes so dont watch for it to tick not worth it, if he chants you he has to be close enough to do so, try to land something on him, disease is my lowest resist at 59 with about 115 in it, assume he has about 30 unless he's uber and or has resist gear, pet is good he might not have room for charm or he'll be expecting it, fear him!!, fear sucks so bad in pvp we cant do anything to break out of it, when he's feared land something anything, if you keep landing dots on him he has to cancel magic himself (3 ticks cast time ) if he buffed himself he has to cast it a few times causeing dmg, in that time nuke him to high heck i have about 1.7 hp now at 59, he'll have alot less ( i'm not a melee bard, yes there are different types of bards, i'm a caster bard, my dmg output and input are lower then the melee bards. </P><P>he can prolly only hit for 30's in melee so he might try to use chants, at that lvl he prolly wont have a good drum and they wont hurt that bad, dont let him run away your in the arena in rathe right so that pvp area isnt that big if he steps outa pvp disqualify him. biggest thing to do is land a poison or disease, and life tap, magic will be high but i'm assuming life tap is hard to resist, when he charms pet it will still bother him for 3 seconds which is good for you hmmm what am i forgetting.... if you get him feared keep him feared at all costs, at that point cancel magic him if you have it ( the three slot one ) then load em up and watch him die. without seeing his equip i cant tell yeah to much on exact tactics nor am i an expert on necros mine is still up and coming</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
