        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> <BR>At level 60, a level 60 bard will own you. Unless he or she is inexperienced or sub-par equipped. Bards have a variety of exploits favouring them. They can use charm pets making them poof (takes 3 ticks). They can run around while using clickable items such as pumices. The best bet is really to use a damage shield potions protected by lots of other buffs, and then drain defensively with deflux (get a mage haste focus item first). </P><P>At 51 you probably stand an even smaller chance, since you lack the fast casting drains. Try the damage shield stuff. Buy a 10-charge kiva's skin of flame from a shaman. </P><P><BR>Zarloth V`Sharatouum<BR>Teir`dal Warlock<BR>Vallon Zek<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
